#
# System configurations
#

All my edited system configuration files (in /) are
stored here and symlinked to proper places.

Packages contain list of packages for bare system with
only X, -ck kernel and -ck nvidia stuff, and some other.

Packages is generated with:
   pacman -Q | grep -v "$(pacman -Qm)" > PACKAGES

X Font setup:
   ! XFT
   Xft.autohint:1
   Xft.lcdfilter:lcddefault
   Xft.hintstyle:hintslight
   Xft.hinting:1
   Xft.antialias:1
   Xft.dpi:96
   Xft.rgba:rgb

